headline: Does Cisco Still Offer Value After Its Strong 33.4% 2025 Year To Date Rally?
summary: How Has Cisco Systems Stock Been Performing Lately Cisco Systems has quietly turned into a strong market performer, and if you are wondering whether the stock is still good value after its recent climb, you are not alone. The company sits in that interesting space where a mature tech giant can still surprise investors who take the time to dig into the numbers. Over the last week Cisco Systems is up 3.7%, it has gained 11.0% over the last month, and its year to date return stands at 33.4%...
